<item>
            <title>[LU-14397] A race between lock enqueue and idle import</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14397</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There is a window after ptlrpc_check_import_is_idle() and setting LUSTRE_IMP_CONNECTING for lock enqueue. The lock get granted on OST and is returned to the client. Server&apos;s lock is destroyed on OST_DISCONNECT.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
